Source: subuser
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Stanislas Leduc <stanislas.leduc@mailoo.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 9), dh-python, python3-dev, python3-setuptools
Standards-Version: 3.9.8
Homepage: http://subuser.org

Package: subuser
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python3:Depends}, git, docker.io
Description: Run programs on Linux with selectively restricted permissions
 Subuser turns a docker container into a normal program, but this program 
 is not fully privileged, it can only access the directory 
 from which it was called.

Package: subuser-doc
Architecture: all
Section: doc
Depends: lsb-base (>= 4.1), $(misc:Depends)
Description: documentation for subuser
 Subuser turns a docker container into a normal program, but this program
 is not fully privileged, it can only access the directory
 from which it was called.
 .
 This package provides documentation for subuser.
